{"tid":2306414,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"日本分級機構CERO盯上Ubisoft，要求解釋《刺客教條 維京紀元》內容與送審版不一致","createTime":"2020-11-30T11:56:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-01T10:28:42.000Z","uid":42675,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"d4f6a59cbb9a13c7215adb35ba5645afac5db366","tid":2306414,"uid":42675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-30T11:56:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SL4ZbxC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSL4ZbxC.jpg&h=9da68a9b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n如果你還有印象，日前我們曾報導《刺客教條：維京紀元》亞洲解封，意外引爆日本Ubisoft與CERO之戰 ，而現在 CERO 名擺著盯上了 Ubisoft，今日針對《刺客教條：維京紀元》送審與販售版的畫面不同，要求 Ubisoft 提出正式的說明。<br />\n<br />\n在日本 Ubisoft 道歉後，隨即又在上週公開了即將於 12 月中釋放解禁 Patch 的消息，這下似乎完全惹毛了 CERO。依據 CERO 過去分級的標準，無論哪一款遊戲，雖然可以見血，但血腥斷肢以及肚破腸流類的畫面是絕對「NG」的項目，並不是分在 Z 級（18歲以上才可遊玩）就什麼都可以。<br />\n<br />\n另外有日本玩家表示，似乎 Ubisoft 昨天起悄悄的在自家的 PC 商城開始販賣了全球版的《刺客教條：維京紀元》（也就是無修正版），但和日本的修正版需要分開購買，暫時沒辦法蓋過原本的日版。<br />\n<br />\nCERO 今日在官網上發表新公告，表示 CERO 發現《刺客教條 維京紀元》雖然在日本分級評為 Z 級，但已經證實 Ubisoft 送審的版本與實際販賣的版本有出入。因此已經正式聯絡 Ubiosft，要求出來說明。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qVSjVZg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqVSjVZg.png&h=86ead45c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n值得注意的是， CERO 這篇公告整篇用詞語氣都非常強勢，以中文的白話文就是「你最好給我出來說清楚！」。雖然 CERO 並沒有明指是針對哪一件事，但 Ubisoft 想用這種先上車後補票的方式來規避審查的確也有可議之處。<br />\n<br />\n當然另一點有趣的是，在上次的戰爭中，CERO 把責任撇的一乾二淨，表示 Ubisoft 根本沒跟他們聯繫，但這次卻主動跳出來指責 Ubisoft 送審版本跟販售版本不同，明顯自打臉。因此誰是和諧版的始作俑者似乎也相當明顯了。<br />\n<br />\n但，人家掌管分級就是有話語權，只怕以後 Ubiosft 的遊戲在日本都不好過了。<br />\n<br />\n醬油:<a href=\"https://www.4gamers.com.tw/news/detail/45749/assassins-creed-valhalla-unexamined-version-sales-in-japan?fbclid=IwAR14O8zGo-O7kykImDmAXcgC64XmgZPUjhvDwsymHdfaG6YBSZioDOeG0gk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.4gamers.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fdetail%2F45749%2Fassassins-creed-valhalla-unexamined-version-sales-in-japan%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR14O8zGo-O7kykImDmAXcgC64XmgZPUjhvDwsymHdfaG6YBSZioDOeG0gk&d=AMq1wuZoRE%2BfxlTDVFm3xPGl%2B26pDsgLotMYn9d4AWI%3D&h=a186a6d9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.4gamers.com.tw/news/detail/45749/assassins-creed-valhalla-unexamined-version-sales-in-japan?fbclid=IwAR14O8zGo-O7kykImDmAXcgC64XmgZPUjhvDwsymHdfaG6YBSZioDOeG0gk</a><br />\n<br />\nCERO真係CLS,彈出彈入你咬我食<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bccdb0dfaf7396e84702af4ca3c14391361ca074","tid":2306414,"uid":66365,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-30T12:13:59.000Z","msg":"日本都要河蟹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05ea6da4b5b3f79fb12b95d68e7d5287062b9aeb","tid":2306414,"uid":165336,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bccdb0dfaf7396e84702af4ca3c14391361ca074","tid":2306414,"uid":66365,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-30T12:13:59.000Z","msg":"日本都要河蟹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-30T12:19:22.000Z","msg":"好出奇？<br />\n知唔知連日本公司出game都可以特別分一個日版出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n日本av都唔俾露個西出黎要打格<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b02d74ed6738c3adeae8b2b8b11b6873367e2921","tid":2306414,"uid":130568,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-30T12:30:02.000Z","msg":"之前仲大把人笑ubi自閹<br />\n<br />\n建議都係唔好跟車太貼<br />\n睇落去就知邊個係人邊個係鬼"},{"pid":"1c8dcb4fdea3cdb9d8f72e168ebfdf8e56de8cc6","tid":2306414,"uid":46669,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"b02d74ed6738c3adeae8b2b8b11b6873367e2921","tid":2306414,"uid":130568,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-30T12:30:02.000Z","msg":"之前仲大把人笑ubi自閹<br />\n<br />\n建議都係唔好跟車太貼<br />\n睇落去就知邊個係人邊個係鬼"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-30T12:37:22.000Z","msg":"今次呢單意思係咪唔夠和諧<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e34b91add5116db096437bb28847abceffa0175e","tid":2306414,"uid":119954,"like":3,"dislike":1,"s